column1: "job_description": "We're looking for an experienced Ecom Google Ads marketer with 5 or more years of experience running ads for Ecommerce stores. You\u2019re someone that has a deep knowledge of Google Ads
column2: enough that you\u2019re able to provide actionable advice for our audience
column3: who are setting up their campaigns for the first time
column4: using our videos for guidance.\nImportant: We are not expecting you to have content writing or scriptwriting experience. We\u2019ll provide clear guides and training on how to write scripts. What we really need is your knowledge and experience!"
